---
title: Thai Yellow Curry & Roasted Veggies with Garlic Rice & Crushed Peanuts
description: Embrace the sunset with this roast veggie and makrut lime leaves (for that touch of citrusy goodness) yellow
curry. Garnish with crushed peanuts to add a bit of nutty crunch and this creamy, spiced dish is done.

